            /**
             * Similar to Die below, but with fixed spot values.
             * Supports passing a diceCount
             *    if not defined, defaults to 1 and returns the value directly.
             *    if defined, returns an array containing the random dice values.
             *
             * D4: (diceCount) => value
             * D6: (diceCount) => value
             * D8: (diceCount) => value
             * D10: (diceCount) => value
             * D12: (diceCount) => value
             * D20: (diceCount) => value
